Title: "Saffron Breeze"
SKU: SB-2024
Size: 20x20 cm
Material: Oil on canvas, stretched on stretcher frame
Created in: Limburg, Netherlands
Price: ‚Ç¨70

This artwork whispers calm through its smooth, flowing strokes of saffron orange. The soft gradients shift delicately, like the warm glow of a sunset melting into the horizon. The surface, smooth and velvety, reflects light gently, creating a serene yet vibrant energy. It‚Äôs a quiet moment captured on canvas ‚Äî simple, pure, and infinitely soothing.

Title: "Amber Haze"
